The paper deals with online learning algorithms that adapt to local patterns in the data, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the design of algorithms and the analysis of their performance, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper deals with the efficient use of resources, which is relevant to cs.SI (Systems and Control).
